<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Uniform Management System | UMS</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      :root {
        --primary: #0d6efd;
        --text-light: #ffffff;
      }
      html, body {
        height: 100%;
        overflow: hidden;
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
      }
      .hero {
        position: relative;
        height: 100vh;
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--text-light);
        background: url('/images/south.jpg') center center / cover no-repeat;
        z-index: 1;
      }
      .hero::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        height: 100%;
        width: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), rgba(6, 51, 118, 0.3));
        z-index: -1;
      }
      .hero-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        max-width: 750px;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
      }
      .hero h1 {
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .hero p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        max-width: 650px;
        margin: 0 auto 35px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      }
      .btn {
        border-radius: 50px;
        padding: 12px 40px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      .btn-primary {
        background-color: var(--primary);
        border: none;
      }
      .btn-primary:hover {
        background-color: #0b5ed7;
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(13, 110, 253, 0.4);
      }
      .btn-outline-light {
        color: #fff;
        border: 2px solid #fff;
      }
      .btn-outline-light:hover {
        background-color: #fff;
        color: #0d6efd;
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
      }
      @keyframes fadeUp {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(30px);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }
      .animate-fade-up {
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
      }
      .animate-fade-up:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
      .animate-fade-up:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
      .animate-fade-up:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero h1 {
          font-size: 2.2rem;
        }
        .hero p {
          font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .btn {
          padding: 10px 28px;
          font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content text-center">
      <h1 class="animate-fade-up" style="font-size: 3.5rem; line-height: 1.2;">
        Simplify Your Uniform Requests
      </h1>
      <p class="animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s; font-size: 1.25rem; max-width: 750px; margin: 20px auto 25px;">
        The Uniform Management System helps organizations efficiently manage
        uniform distribution, requests, and inventory reducing manual work and saving time.
      </p>
      <p class="animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.45s; font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 40px;">
        Empower your team with a modern, automated, and user-friendly platform designed to keep every uniform request organized and effortless.
      </p>
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-5">
          <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right me-2"></i>Login
        </a>
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-5">
          <i class="bi bi-person-plus me-2"></i>Create Account
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
